# Protect OnInit and load arming

Startup scanning / timer arming is working after careful in-game fixes.
**Do not modify `OnInit`, `HandleGameResume`, `ScheduleBootArm`, `EnsurePlayerCombatQuest`, or the killscan `OnTimer` re-arm order unless the user explicitly discusses and approves the change first.**

